{% macro ec_full(contract) -%}
## The four-stage audit gauntlet (verbatim)

This is the bar your work will be graded against. Every claim you make
about your work — every subtask declaration, every doer self-audit,
every checker verdict — should map back onto these stage cards. The
audit is the truth-of-record; everything upstream of it that contradicts
the bar will surface as a failed cycle.

{{ _stage_block(contract.local_ci) }}

{{ _stage_block(contract.rubric) }}

{{ _stage_block(contract.standards) }}

{{ _stage_block(contract.behavior) }}
